---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog - Rob Spain | School BCBA Insights
description: Insights, strategies, and systematic approaches for school-based behavior analysis from Rob Spain, BCBA.
---

<header class="section-premium" style="padding-top: 140px; background: var(--gradient-hero); color: white; text-align: center;">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="display-1">School BCBA <span class="hero-title-gradient">Blog</span></h1>
        <p class="body-large" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); max-width: 700px; margin: 1rem auto;">
            Insights and systematic approaches to transform school behavior systems.
        </p>
    </div>
</header>

<section class="section-premium">
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Featured/Latest Post Highlight -->
        {% if collections.blog | length > 0 %}
        {% set latestPost = collections.blog | reverse | first %}
        <div class="latest-post-highlight animate-fade-up">
            <div class="highlight-card card-premium">
                <div class="highlight-image">
                    {% if latestPost.data.image %}
                        <img src="{{ latestPost.data.image }}" alt="{{ latestPost.data.title }}">
                    {% else %}
                        <div class="placeholder-icon"><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i></div>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
                <div class="highlight-content">
                    <span class="section-badge-premium">Latest Insights</span>
                    <h2 class="text-h1">{{ latestPost.data.title }}</h2>
                    <p class="body-large">{{ latestPost.data.description or latestPost.templateContent | striptags | truncate(200) }}</p>
                    <a href="{{ latestPost.url }}" class="btn-primary-premium">Read Full Story <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        {% endif %}

        <div class="cards-grid-premium" id="blog-posts" style="margin-top: 4rem;">
            {% for post in collections.blog | reverse %}
            {% if loop.index > 1 %}
            <article class="card-premium">
                <div class="card-icon-premium">
                    {% if post.data.image %}
                        <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 1rem;">
                    {% else %}
                        <i class="fas fa-book-open"></i>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
                <h3 class="card-title-premium">{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
                <div style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">
                    {{ post.date.toDateString() }}
                </div>
                <p class="card-description-premium">
                    {{ post.data.description or post.templateContent | striptags | truncate(150) }}
                </p>
                <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="card-link-premium">Read More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
            </article>
            {% endif %}
            {% else %}
            <div style="grid-column: 1 / -1; text-align: center; padding: 2rem;">
                <h3>No posts yet.</h3>
                <p>Check back soon for updates!</p>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
.latest-post-highlight {
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
}

.highlight-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 4rem !important;
}

.highlight-image {
    border-radius: 24px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
}

.highlight-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 400px;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
}

.highlight-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .highlight-card {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        padding: 2rem !important;
        gap: 2rem;
    }
    .highlight-image img {
        height: 250px;
    }
}
</style>